<https://linked.data.gov.au/org/qld-daff> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Department of Agriculture and Fisheries (DAF) was officially dissolved and replaced by the Department of Primary Industries (DPI) on 1 November 2024, due to machinery of government changes.\n\nFormerly known as the Department of Agriculture and Fisheries.\n\nWe ensure that Queensland’s primary industries—the essential backbone of our economy and communities—are productive, profitable and sustainable for future generations.\n\nWe do this by connecting industries, the community and government to grow our economy, protect our primary industries from biosecurity threats and support rural communities."@en .
